    <h3 class="hed">Why Benjamin Netanyahu Loves the European Far-Right</h3>
</a>
<div class="dek-heading -excerpt">
    <p class="dek">Recent spats aside, Israel’s right-wing government sees the illiberal nationalist leaders of Poland and Hungary as natural allies. They share a hostility toward human rights, Enlightenment values, and the European Union.</p>
